## Proposed Changes

### [Server]

#### [MODIFY] [auth.controller.ts](file:///c:/Apps/Leave%20Tracker/server/src/controllers/auth.controller.ts)
- Refactor the login validation logic to handle cases where the password is a phone number in either `07...` or `254...` format.
- If `requiresPasswordChange` is true, the server will try comparing the entered password (both raw and normalized) against the stored password hash and the stored phone number.
